ðŸ”¹ Core Feature: Multi-Step User Form

Create a super-friendly, guided, spoon-feeding flow for user onboarding.
It should collect the following information:

Basic Details

Full Name

Phone Number

Email

Date of Birth

Height

Weight

Medical Questions (Yes/No + Optional detail field)

Do you have Diabetes? (Type 1 / Type 2)

High Blood Pressure?

Cholesterol issues?

Any surgeries?

For women:

PCOD/PCOS?

Any gynecological surgery?

Joint or bone-related injuries?

Any chronic diseases?

Any other medical conditions?

UX Requirements

Each question should be simple, one-by-one or grouped cleanly.

Use:

Toggle switches

Radio buttons

Simple inputs

Optional textarea if they choose "Yes"

Provide progress indication (ex: Step 1/5)

ðŸ”¹ Output After Form Completion

