Beginner / intermediate

Weekly schedule

Rest days

Simple, accurate, safe exercises

Clear formatting

2. Personalized Meal Plan

Based on:

Weight goals

Health issues (BP, diabetes, PCOS, etc.)

Veg / non-veg preference

Clean card layout

Easy-to-read meals (Breakfast / Lunch / Dinner / Snacks)

UI Requirements for Plans

Use clear section cards

Soft shadows

Suitable spacing

Simple icons

Easy to scan and understand

